{"tid":545884,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做女人真係好苦","createTime":"2018-01-31T03:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T12:08:02.000Z","uid":51739,"like":36,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"662d02a633d917e61c65fbe81abb8d6036bdf3a2","tid":545884,"uid":51739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"番工做嘢要做到萬事俱備。<br />\n啲同事乜嘢都鍾意問你意見，所以就算心情有幾差都要即刻俾到解決方法佢地。<br />\n老細又會冇啦啦棟喺你面前問之前啲projects做到咩status...真係心血少啲都死。<br />\nLunch走去買餸（都算係可以relax下），辛辛苦苦捱到放工就趕住番屋企做家務同煮飯，等老公收工接埋阿仔番屋企有飯食。<br />\n跟住就開始忙湊仔，餵飯，玩，執玩具，執衫仔同佢沖涼，氹瞓覺。之後就係洗碗執頭執尾，好喇差唔多一點終於可以沖涼做下自己嘢。<br />\n點解好似冇提過個老公？因為佢隱左形，剩係掛住玩電話，但係又會間唔中話下你做老婆可唔可以溫柔啲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我明白男女係不平等，但我付出嘅同時其實都想有個人喺身邊支持下，唔幫手都氹下啦。連呢啲少少嘅嘢都冇，個人真係越來越冇心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ae64e30ef91f359d41ef44f0e9713f01ddd4e7","tid":545884,"uid":45627,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:26:41.000Z","msg":"其實你都有返全職<br />\n點解洗碗執頭執尾呢啲工作唔可以由老公分擔一下?<br />\n你已經負責買餸煮飯, 另一半洗碗都好平常<br />\n<br />\n男人返工係辛苦, 但你都同樣要返工啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35379cab4e64aa85fab819af836e77d0c626c894","tid":545884,"uid":21202,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"溝通下"},{"pid":"35e274985bcb088c47e7f706e37e25200bf4c499","tid":545884,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"有無試過屌柒佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e288c7a6348c0feb3b19fc5ba35e1fe57c0365ee","tid":545884,"uid":51739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b3ae64e30ef91f359d41ef44f0e9713f01ddd4e7","tid":545884,"uid":45627,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:26:41.000Z","msg":"其實你都有返全職<br />\n點解洗碗執頭執尾呢啲工作唔可以由老公分擔一下?<br />\n你已經負責買餸煮飯, 另一半洗碗都好平常<br />\n<br />\n男人返工係辛苦, 但你都同樣要返工啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:33:42.000Z","msg":"有時都會肯幫下手但主力就係我負責。如果要求佢幫手，佢會係捨難取易咁做下家務... 但就一定唔會洗碗。我洗到對手都爆晒擦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ae7f192d9ef1d7b7b276fca87199e5f5e4c7fe","tid":545884,"uid":161421,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"唔好生第2個囉, <br />\n<br />\n呢d男人踢都唔郁,仲要話返你轉頭.自己睇路...."},{"pid":"fb2b540caad444299f4b4718f5041559b16799d7","tid":545884,"uid":51739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"35379cab4e64aa85fab819af836e77d0c626c894","tid":545884,"uid":21202,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"溝通下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:34:27.000Z","msg":"一溝通就鬧交，之後仲要氹番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777f668bf35a2d47afdb219ca64e31f4c6b42b73","tid":545884,"uid":51739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35e274985bcb088c47e7f706e37e25200bf4c499","tid":545884,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"有無試過屌柒佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"只會換來一場大交，好辛苦㗎"},{"pid":"d727aa0b523ac01c0b59d9010f696a7c8309b8e8","tid":545884,"uid":51739,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b4ae7f192d9ef1d7b7b276fca87199e5f5e4c7fe","tid":545884,"uid":161421,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:33:44.000Z","msg":"唔好生第2個囉, <br />\n<br />\n呢d男人踢都唔郁,仲要話返你轉頭.自己睇路...."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"唉，大男人真係好難頂"},{"pid":"02ed8db08ed1710a86204d3372b426af48f35b91","tid":545884,"uid":70417,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"離婚帶